  "texts": [
    "Thus, in formulating ethical standards for trustworthy AI, we would recommend focusing on the key dimensions of competence and warmth.",
    "For example, in developing and deploying AI applications, it is critical to conduct an ethical evaluation based on their competence and warmth.",
    "This evaluation ensures that the applications are functionally effective and possess benevolent intentions toward humanity.",
    "In addition, as AI technology advances, its potential to infringe upon human rights intensifies, underscoring the increasing importance of evaluating its warmth.",
    "Recognizing how individual characteristics influence trust in AI can guide the development of personalized and adaptive AI interaction strategies."
  ],
